- provide(:title, 'Agent')

.jumbotron.black-bg#agent1
  .container.text-center#header-threshold
    %h1 BECOME AN AGENT.
    %p Earning money couldn't be easier.

.jumbotron.white-bg
  .container.text-center
    %h2.purple
      JOINING THE
      %b A
      TEAM
    %p Don't worry about listing prices, negotiations, and finding your own sellers and buyers - we at RideSnap take care of that for you. Simply coordinate with a buyer, give a test drive, and earn money.
    %hr
    %p Getting started is easy! Just do the following 3 steps:
    %ol
      %li.purple Tell us about yourself and provide the necessary documents.
      %li.purple Wait for clearance and approval.
      %li.purple You're set!
    %p
      %small You'll then be ready to photograph cars and schedule test drives with potential buyers!

.jumbotron.whitesmoke-bg
  .container.text-center
    %h2.purple Agent Responsibilities
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-xs-12
        %p
          %b REQUIREMENTS
        %s &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        %ul
          %li Your own car
          %li iPhone or Android smartphone
          %li Driver's license and valid insurance
          %li Clean driving record
          %li Attentive to details and always on time
          %li Friendly, outgoing, genuinely kind
          %li Must be 18 or older
      .col-md-6.col-xs-12
        %p
          %b DUTIES
        %s &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        %ul
          %li Be the face of the company by interacting with customers
          %li Make up to 20% of the profit RideSnap makes!
          %li Choose when you want to work
          %li Manage the cars we assign to you
          %li Coordinate test drives around the buyer's schedule

.jumbotron.white-bg
  .container.text-center
    %h2.purple Apply Today.
    %br
    %br
    = form_for User.new, url: agent_users_path, html: {class: 'form-inline', id: 'vehicle-inspection', role: 'form'} do |f|
      .form-group
        = f.label :name, nil, class: 'sr-only'
        = f.text_field :name, placeholder: 'Full Name', class: 'form-control'
      .form-group
        = f.label :zip_code, nil, class: 'sr-only'
        = f.text_field :zip_code, placeholder: 'Zip Code', class: 'form-control'
      %br
      .form-group
        = f.label :phone, nil, class: 'sr-only'
        = f.text_field :phone, placeholder: 'Phone', class: 'form-control phone'
      .form-group
        = f.label :email, nil, class: 'sr-only'
        = f.text_field :email, placeholder: 'Email', class: 'form-control'
      / %br
      / .form-group
      /   = f.label :reference, nil, class: 'sr-only'
      /   = f.text_field :reference, placeholder: 'Referred By (optional)', class: 'form-control'
      %br
      .form-group
        = f.submit 'Apply', class: 'btn btn-purple btn-wide'
